subs.text: How about a 2-hour trial for Trump on a Saturday in April.

I got my Covid vaccine today. I was really lucky, I had signed up to be notified from a local pharmacy, and I got their email last night a few minutes after they sent it. Signed up right away and at 3PM today I got my first dose of the Moderna vaccine. So far no side-effects. Two life-changing events in one day. Not bad! :boom:
